des:
Ask for Eagles Facts to learn a fact about the Eagles Super Bowl history. This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by the Eagles.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Eagles Facts" or "Alexa, open Eagles Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop".

We hope you enjoy this Eagles Facts skill! If you liked it, please rate us with some stars! Your feedback is important to us. Also, you may like some of our other skills, for education and safety try, New Jersey Hunter, and New Jersey Boater. For more fun, try our Sports Trivia game. 

Thanks again, and Go Birds!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
